Record Class JpaEntityModel

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.kivojenko.spring.forge.jpa.model.model.JpaEntityModel
Record Components:
element - the entity type element
entityType - the JavaPoet class name of the entity
jpaId - information about the entity's ID field
packages - package names for generated classes
requirements - configuration requirements for the entity
env - the processing environment
public record JpaEntityModel(TypeElement element, com.squareup.javapoet.ClassName entityType, JpaId jpaId, JpaEntityPackageNames packages, JpaEntityModelRequirements requirements, ProcessingEnvironment env) extends Record
Represents a JPA entity model with information needed for code generation.
